### Hadith 3:105

*Narrated Anas bin Malik:*

The Prophet said, "There will be no town which Ad-Dajjal will not enter
except Mecca and Medina, and there will be no entrance (road) (of both
Mecca and Medina) but the angels will be standing in rows guarding it
against him, and then Medina will shake with its inhabitants thrice
(i.e. three earth-quakes will take place) and Allah will expel all the
nonbelievers and the hypocrites from it."

